---
---

<!-- TIPOGRAFÍA -->
<section class="wrap" id="tipo">
  <div class="tag"><span class="n">05</span> Atoms · Tipografía — mono base + display modular</div>
  <h2 style="margin-bottom:var(--sp-11)">Voz</h2>
  <div class="typegrid">
    <div class="typecell">
      <div class="label-sm">
        Display · modular sobre grilla <span class="pill">Syne · confirmada</span>
      </div>
      <div class="specimen">Aa<br />Gg</div>
      <p style="font-size:var(--fs-sm); color:var(--muted); margin-top:var(--sp-6)">
        Construida sobre módulos, no humanista. Coherente con "el texto como arquitectura".
        Definitiva: <b style="color:var(--line)">Syne</b>, dentro del lane modular/experimental, sobre
        la grilla del sistema.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="typecell">
      <div class="label-sm">Mono base · IBM Plex Mono / Iosevka</div>
      <div class="scale mono-spec">
        <div><span class="px">700</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-bold)">Discovery cerrado</span></div>
        <div><span class="px">500</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-medium)">Arquitectura / UX</span></div>
        <div><span class="px">400</span><span>Sistema de diseño bloqueado en v3</span></div>
        <div>
          <span class="px">400i</span><span style="font-style:italic">// el comentario también es diseño</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="px">300</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-light); color:var(--muted)"
            >$ git commit -m "tokens definitivos"</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="label-sm" style="margin-top:var(--sp-12)">Pesos · interlineado · tracking</div>
  <div class="tgrid3">
    <div class="typecell">
      <div class="label-sm">Pesos · <code>--fw-*</code></div>
      <div class="wsample mono-spec">
        <div><span class="wn">300</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-light)">light · titular tenue</span></div>
        <div><span class="wn">400</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-regular)">regular · cuerpo</span></div>
        <div><span class="wn">500</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-medium)">medium · énfasis</span></div>
        <div><span class="wn">600</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-semibold)">semibold · etiqueta</span></div>
        <div><span class="wn">700</span><span style="font-weight:var(--fw-bold)">bold · jerarquía</span></div>
        <div>
          <span class="wn">800</span><span style="font-family:var(--display); font-weight:var(--fw-black); text-transform:uppercase">black · display</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="typecell">
      <div class="label-sm">Interlineado · <code>--lh-*</code></div>
      <div class="lhsample">
        <p style="line-height:var(--lh-solid)"><span class="lhn">1.0 solid</span>El texto<br />como arquitectura</p>
        <p style="line-height:var(--lh-display)"><span class="lhn">1.18 display</span>El texto<br />como arquitectura</p>
        <p style="line-height:var(--lh-body)"><span class="lhn">1.55 body</span>El texto que se lee, con aire suficiente para el cuerpo largo.</p>
        <p style="line-height:var(--lh-loose)"><span class="lhn">1.7 loose</span>El texto que respira, para bloques densos o de soporte.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="typecell">
      <div class="label-sm">Tracking · <code>--tr-*</code></div>
      <div class="trsample">
        <div><span class="trn">-.02 tightest</span><span style="letter-spacing:var(--tr-tightest)">SISTEMA</span></div>
        <div><span class="trn">.01 normal</span><span style="letter-spacing:var(--tr-normal)">SISTEMA</span></div>
        <div><span class="trn">.08 caps</span><span style="letter-spacing:var(--tr-caps)">SISTEMA</span></div>
        <div><span class="trn">.14 caps-xl</span><span style="letter-spacing:var(--tr-caps-xl)">SISTEMA</span></div>
        <div><span class="trn">.22 widest</span><span style="letter-spacing:var(--tr-widest)">SISTEMA</span></div>
        <div><span class="trn">.3 mega</span><span style="letter-spacing:var(--tr-mega)">SISTEMA</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.9em;
    color: var(--c-blue-text);
  }
  .tgrid3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--sp-px);
    background: var(--overlay);
    border: var(--bw) solid var(--overlay);
    margin-top: var(--sp-5);
  }
  .tgrid3 .typecell {
    padding: var(--sp-9);
  }
  .wsample > div,
  .trsample > div {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--sp-6);
    padding: var(--sp-3) 0;
    border-bottom: var(--bw) solid var(--overlay);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--txt);
  }
  .wn,
  .trn,
  .lhn {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-3xs);
    color: var(--muted);
    flex: none;
    width: 70px;
  }
  .trn {
    width: 92px;
  }
  .lhsample p {
    color: var(--txt);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    max-width: none;
  }
  .lhn {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
    width: auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .tgrid3 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

